---
title: Contact
class: "page__contact"
---
<section class="site__content wrap padding-top">
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="grid__col grid__col--3-of-12">

      <h2>Notice</h2>
      <p>After a year-long sabbatical, I am now available for freelance work. Shoot me an email and let's get started!</p>

    </div>
    <div class="grid__col grid__col--6-of-12 grid__col--push-1-of-12">

      <h2>I'd like to get to know you.</h2>
      <p>Whether you want to start a new design project, ask me a question, or just chat, feel free to email me. I promise I'll answer.</p>
      <p>Email: <a href="mailto:studio@devinhalladay.com?Subject=I%20want%20to%20talk%20about...&Body=Hey%20Devin%21">studio@devinhalladay.com</a></p>
      <h3>You can also find me on...</h3>
      <p>
        <% data.links.each_with_index do |link, index| %>
          <a href="<%= link.url %>"><%= link.name %></a><% unless index == link.length %><br><% end %>
        <% end %>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
